| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3541 — Recovery Inhibition (hunters)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: cc8190d0-13aa-5b40-9f6e-e4004ae80e84"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
